msgid "Podman Pod Generator"
msgstr "Podman Pod Generator"

msgid "Configure your pod — get ready-to-use Kubernetes YAML for podman play kube."
msgstr "Konfiguriere deinen Pod — bekomme fertiges Kubernetes YAML für podman play kube."

msgid "Quick Start — Predefined Stacks"
msgstr "Schnellstart — fertige Stacks"

msgid "Select stack..."
msgstr "Stack auswählen..."

msgid "Fills the form completely — including correct 127.0.0.1 connections."
msgstr "Füllt das Formular komplett aus — inkl. richtiger 127.0.0.1-Verbindungen."

msgid "Pod Settings"
msgstr "Pod-Einstellungen"

msgid "Advanced Pod Options"
msgstr "Erweiterte Pod-Optionen"

msgid "Affects the deployment guide"
msgstr "Beeinflusst die Deployment-Anleitung"

